com.intel.fightclub.dialog.observer

Class WorkoutChoiceObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.observer.EventObserver<WorkoutChoice>
      • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.observer.WorkoutChoiceObserver

  • @ThreadSafe
public final class WorkoutChoiceObserver
extends EventObserver<WorkoutChoice>
    Responsible for keeping track of the workout choice in the DialogLib. Workout choice updates can be triggered both by the UI and CUI, so the mediator is centralizing updates and delivering callbacks to interested clients. This class is meant to be one of those clients.
